{
  "stem": "19218.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 191.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sure.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do not recall whether it took two days, two nights, three nights.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I honestly cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But of course, there was no place to sit down or to lie down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it was just really cramped in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I-- there could have been a bucket for-- for waste, but-- but unfortunately, if it was, it was filled up immediately.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was waste all over, human waste all over.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did not get any water or any food to eat on that ride, so of course, people died in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When we arrived, I mean, they just take-- I guess maybe those people were the lucky ones.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was impossible to escape.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, the boxcars were just locked up and we had no tools or we didn't bring any the luggage with us even.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So of course, we-- we had nothing to escape there, so many people had died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We were all starved.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was winter, so of course the first thing we were looking for a little bit of snow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We also had immediate contact not only with the soldiers, and the soldiers were all just mad dogs.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Those were-- those were the SS.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They were constantly screaming and yelling.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And although we did understand German, but-- but the words they used, of course, were strange to me anyway and I didn't know them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I couldn't understand the words they were saying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then the-- the-- there were prisoners there, too, which were already in the camps, a special breed of prisoners because they knew the faith, what is going to happen to most of the people.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they just said, at least to-- when we were separated-- don't worry, you'll be OK.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
